  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Fit to body</measure>
    <time_frame>14 +/- 2 days</time_frame>
    <description>Subjects will evaluate the fit to body for each product by answering the question &quot;How was the base plates ability to fit the body contours in the area around the stoma?&quot;
The question is answered with a 5-point scale ranging from Very Poor - Very Good (1-5), where the very poor (1) is the worst possible score and very good (5) is the best possible score.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
